title: Trump moves to expel some 57,000 Hondurans
text:
Trump moves to expel some 57,000 Hondurans 12:20am BST - 01:39
The Trump administration says it will end temporary protections for immigrants in the U.S. from Honduras on Jan. 5, 2020, leaving potentially 57,000 people vulnerable.
